paths: Obvious exits: east, southeast, south, northwest
description: This is obviously another area the goblins have claimed as living quarters.  Piles of rags line the walls all about.  A fire pit smolders in the chamber's center, giving off the rank smell of burning hair.  All sorts of scraps and trinkets litter the ground around the pit's perimeter.
title: [Sea Caverns, Sleeping Quarters]
